description:
Today Scientist are experimenting with what people are eating. Meat products are being developed in the laboratory to satisfy the craving for flesh foods and at the same time not omit too many greenhouse gasses. The source for these experiments are animal fetuses. Is this the future for food? Instead of growing meat in labs let us cooperate with God and grow our food in the garden as God intended when he placed man in Eden. Join us on our journey to help people to continue the vision God has given.
Contact us at gardenevangelist@gmail.com
Happy Planting!
